{"tid":1077836,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"電影版《大叔的愛》香港取景 暑假上映","createTime":"2019-03-26T00:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T00:37:41.000Z","uid":41343,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2570ac642d4a7caf0ac9b6119acfb40cc988cb","tid":1077836,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:37:41.000Z","msg":"日本BL神劇《大叔的愛》去年掀起熱潮，早前已宣佈添食開拍電影版，會由原班人馬演出，安排今年夏天上映。<br />\n<br />\n電影版《大叔的愛》繼續圍繞田中圭飾演的春田，劇集版講到他與林遣都扮演的阿牧有情人終成眷屬，展開同居生活，有估計電影會交代春田被調派到海外工作，雖然片商一直對內容大賣關子，但吉田鋼太郎飾演的部長黑澤武藏就相隔逾三個月再更新IG，繼上次貼了上海夜景後，今次則上載從香港山頂拍下的夜景照片，並提到#在香港，此Po似乎是暗示電影版是在香港取景。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190325/59407726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59407726&d=Fb7z1ilWoLc7MobAJ3fbq4oP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=432808ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190325%2F59407726&h=5ba1a259\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190325/59407726</a>"}]}